$ Oracle: Analytic functions LAG and LEAD

The → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/select/analytic/lag-lead[analytic function] `LAG` returns a value of a «previous», `LEAD` a value of a «following» record.

gh|Oracle-Patterns|/SQL/select/analytical_functions/lag-vs-lead.sql||

The previous SQL statement returns
code {
T          LEAD_1     LAG_1      LEAD_3     LAG_3     
---------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------
one        two                   four                 
two        three      one        five                 
three      four       two                             
four       five       three                 one       
five                  four                  two   
code }

